description: Onboards a tenant in Azure Active Directory Connect Health.

onboarded.description: Indicates if the tenant is already onboarded to Azure Active Directory Connect Health.

devopsttl.description: The date and time, in UTC, till when the tenant data can be seen by Microsoft through Azure portal.

globaladminsemail.description: The list of global administrators for the tenant.

tenantinquarantine.description: Indicates if data collection for this tenant is disabled or not.

pkscertificate.description: The certificate associated with the tenant to onboard data to Azure Active Directory Connect Health.

disabledreason.description: The reason due to which the tenant was disabled in Azure Active Directory Connect Health.

aadlicense.description: The Azure Active Directory license of the tenant.

lastverified.description: The date and time, in UTC, when the tenant onboarding status in Azure Active Directory Connect Health was last verified.

api_version.description: The version of the API to be used with the client request.

onboardingallowed.description: Indicates if the tenant is allowed to  onboard to Azure Active Directory Connect Health.

agentautoupdate.description: Indicates if the tenant is configured to automatically receive updates for Azure Active Directory Connect Health client side features.

createddate.description: The date, in UTC, when the tenant was onboarded to Azure Active Directory Connect Health.

disabled.description: Indicates if the tenant is disabled in Azure Active Directory Connect Health.

initialdomain.description: The initial domain of the tenant.

countrylettercode.description: The country letter code of the tenant.

aadpremium.description: Indicate if the tenant has Azure Active Directory Premium license or not.

privatepreviewtenant.description: Indicates if the tenant has signed up for private preview of Azure Active Directory Connect Health features.

lastdisabled.description: The date and time, in UTC, when the tenant was last disabled in Azure Active Directory Connect Health.

alertsuppressiontimeinmins.description: The time in minutes after which an alert will be auto-suppressed.

consentedtomicrosoftdevops.description: Indicates if the tenant data can be seen by Microsoft through Azure portal.
